    "source_code": "#include <stdio.h>\nlong factorial( long );\n\nint main()\n{\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0int i;\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0for ( i = 1; i <= 10; i++ )\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0printf( \"%2d! = %ld\\n\", i, factorial( i ) );\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0return 0;\n}\n\nlong factorial( long number )\n{\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0if ( number <= 1 )\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0return 1;\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0else\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0return ( number * factorial( number - 1 ) );\n}"
